<p class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">L&apos;utilitaire &quot;</span><span class="rvts41">Integration</span><span class="rvts8">&quot; </span><img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle; padding : 1px;" src="imgspec/NouvelElement1400.png"><span class="rvts8"> permet de cr&#xE9;er des </span><span class="rvts9">actions</span><span class="rvts8"> permettant de r&#xE9;aliser automatiquement des &quot;</span><span class="rvts9">Op&#xE9;rations</span><span class="rvts8">&quot; de modifications de vos documents en fonction :</span></p>
<ul style="text-indent: 0px; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 0 24px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: disc;">
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">De </span><span class="rvts9">conditions</span><span class="rvts8">.</span></li>
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">De </span><span class="rvts9">r&#xE8;gles personnalisables</span><span class="rvts8">.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">Vous pouvez enregistrer des favoris de modifications afin de ne pas avoir &#xE0; recr&#xE9;er des </span><span class="rvts9">Listes de crit&#xE8;res de modification</span><span class="rvts8">.</span></p>
<p class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8"><br></span></p>
<p class="rvps26"><img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle; padding : 1px;" src="imgspec/NouvelElement1399.png"><span class="rvts7"> &#xA0;</span></p>
<p class="rvps26"><span class="rvts7"><br></span></p>
<p class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">L&apos;interface pr&#xE9;sente 4 zones permettant d&apos;effectuer les traitements des fichiers :</span></p>
<ul style="text-indent: 0px; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 0 24px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: disc;">
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">Une zone de </span><span class="rvts9">s&#xE9;lection</span><span class="rvts8"> des fichiers ou des r&#xE9;pertoires &#xE0; prendre en compte.</span></li>
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">Une zone dans laquelle sont ajout&#xE9;s et list&#xE9;s les crit&#xE8;res de modification comportant les conditions et op&#xE9;rations souhait&#xE9;es.</span></li>
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">Une zone dans laquelle on s&#xE9;lectionne les </span><span class="rvts9">conditions &#xE0; respecter</span><span class="rvts8">.</span></li>
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">Une zone dans laquelle on s&#xE9;lectionne les </span><span class="rvts9">op&#xE9;rations &#xE0; ex&#xE9;cuter</span><span class="rvts8">.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">Un onglet </span><span class="rvts9">Options</span><span class="rvts8"> permet :</span></p>
<ul style="text-indent: 0px; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 0 24px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: disc;">
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">De configurer les </span><span class="rvts9">comportements</span><span class="rvts8"> des fichiers lors du lancement de l&apos;utilitaire.</span></li>
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">De sp&#xE9;cifier des </span><span class="rvts9">emplacements</span><span class="rvts8"> de sauvegarde et recherche.</span></li>
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">De g&#xE9;rer les </span><span class="rvts9">rapports</span><span class="rvts8"> (emplacement ...).</span></li>
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">De g&#xE9;rer le param&#xE9;trage des </span><span class="rvts9">tables</span><span class="rvts8"> (point d&apos;ancrage, position ...).</span></li>
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">De sp&#xE9;cifier la prise en compte des </span><span class="rvts9">configurations</span><span class="rvts8">.</span></li>
<li class="rvps26"><span class="rvts8">D&apos;initialiser les </span><span class="rvts9">r&#xE8;gles de nommage</span><span class="rvts8">.</span></li>
